latestPosts.caption:
✨ Presenting our “Women-Owned Business of the Month”: @rups.creations.09 founded by the incredibly driven Rupali from Maharashtra!

A third-gen creative in her own right, Rupali turned her passion for DIY fashion into a thriving homegrown label, repurposing sarees, hand-stitching one-of-a-kind pieces, and building a community that values thoughtful, sustainable style.

From styling tutorials to custom creations, every post on @rups.creations.09 reflects her craftsmanship and vision. Don’t miss her upcoming drops—featuring limited-edition, handcrafted outfits designed with heart and heritage.

Follow her journey, support a growing woman-led business, and maybe even find your next favorite outfit 💛

✨ “Let me tell you about a place that’s truly special to me – 18Foreverrr!” ✨

They’ve carved a name for themselves with two standout offerings:

1️⃣ Customization like no other!
From stylish western wear to twinning outfits for your brother’s big day, or even a traditional blouse for your mom’s cherished Paithani saree – they can customize anything with finesse.

2️⃣ A curated boutique collection
Think elegant sarees, stunning lehengas, and rich dress materials – all handpicked with a strong belief in quality over quantity. You won’t find racks overflowing, but what you do find is truly exclusive.

And you know what makes 18Foreverrr even more special for me?
💖 It’s where I did my very first internship! This place is more than fashion – it’s full of passion, creativity, and heart.

📍 Visit us : Near Vits hotel, Vedant nagar, Chh. Sambhajinagar.

📱 Follow for more such videos @18foreverrr_thedesignerstore
